{"word":"Preaching","slug":"preaching","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Preaching</b> The act of exhorting, prophesying, reproving, teaching.<br/> Solomon called preacher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=1&verse=1'>Ecc 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=1&verse=12'>Ecc 1:12</a><br/> Noah called preacher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=5'>2Pe 2:5</a><br/> Sitting while<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=1'>Mat 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=20'>Luk 4:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=3'>Luk 5:3</a><br/> Moses, slow of speech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=12'>Exo 4:12</a><br/> Preaching repentance:<br/> - By John the Baptist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=2'>Mat 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=4'>Mar 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=15'>Mar 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=3'>Luk 3:3</a> <br/> - By Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=17'>Mat 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=15'>Mar 1:15</a> <br/> - By the apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=12'>Mar 6:12</a> <br/> &#187;The Gospel of the Kingdom of God,&#171; the subject of Christ's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=15'>Mar 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2&verse=2'>Mar 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=1'>Luk 8:1</a><br/> Christ crucified and risen, the burden of Paul's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=3'>Act 17:3</a><br/> Effective:<br/> - By Azariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=15'>2Ch 15:15</a> <br/> - By Jonah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=10'>Jon 3:10</a> <br/> - By Peter and other apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=41'>Act 2:41</a> <br/> - By Philip<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=12'>Act 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=38'>Act 8:38</a> <br/> - By Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=20'>Act 9:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=43'>Act 13:43</a><br/><a href='S:Revivals, Religious'>Revivals</a> <br/> Impenitence under:<br/> - Of Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=10'>2Ch 16:10</a> <br/> - Of Ahab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=18&verse=26'>2Ch 18:26</a> <br/> - Of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=46'>Act 13:46</a><br/><a href='S:Obduracy'>Obduracy</a>; <a href='S:Minister, A Sacred Teacher'>Minister, A Sacred Teacher</a>; <a href='S:Call, Personal'>Call, Personal</a> <br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=26'>Mat 11:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=2'>Psa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=21'>Luk 10:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=18'>1Co 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=21'>1Co 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=23'>1Co 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=29'>1Co 1:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&cha